## Core doctrine

1. Do not flatten unlike functions early.
2. Treat bgz17 as HEEL, not universal truth.
3. Split at least into QK / V / Gate / UD.
4. Keep field distinct from sweep distinct from bus.
5. Treat style as collapse policy.
6. Preserve contradiction as structure.
7. Compile thought into structure before text.

